window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>The Aspect: The Complete Series</i> is the culmination of the four books in The Aspect series.<br> <br> Follow Tempest's journey of self-discovery in a threatening world of savage beasts and unknown horrors from cross-dimensional planes.<br> <br> Once he discovers his true identity and purpose, he'll be thrust into the world's political center, deciding the fate of thousands of souls.<br> <br> But he will not do it alone. He'll surround himself with beautiful allies who'll fight at his side to support his cause.<br> <br> However, assassins, political rivals, and even the gods themselves look to thwart any change to the status quo.</p> <p>This set includes the following books:</p> <ul> <li><i>The Aspect: Journey to the Firegrove</i></li> <li><i>The Aspect: The Cessation's Harbinger</i></li> <li><i>The Aspect: Escape From Chernobog</i></li> <li><i>The Aspect: The Divine Terminus</i></li> </ul>"; 
